      "role": "user",
      "content": "right but if you look at the actual trends, isn't it pretty obvious that the incentive to work just isn't there anymore because of these programs? like, why bother with a job if the government is basically covering your costs anyway? it seems like the data is pretty much screaming that the safety net is the main driver here.",
